T02TD3635E:250b-1: ma h'a ba la s'a dha nam /
T02TD3635E:250b-4: khro bo'i rgyal po stobs po che la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD3635E:250b-5: sngon dug sungs pa'i cho gas stong pa nyid kyis mthar padma dkar po dang nyi ma la h'um yig las byung ba'i stobs bo che zhal gcig pa phyag bzhi pa sku mdog thams cad dmar po //
T02TD3635E:250b-6: dbu skra dmar ser gyen du 'khyil pa /
T02TD3635E:250b-8: phag g-yas pa gnyis kyis dbyug pa dkar po dang /
T02TD3635E:250b-10: phyag g-yon pa gnyis kyis phyag 'tshal ba'i tshul dang /
T02TD3635E:250b-11: zhags pa dang bcas pa'i sdigs mdzub mdzad pa /
T02TD3635E:250b-12: stag gi pags pa'i sham thabs can /
T02TD3635E:250b-15: nyi ma'i dkyil 'khor gyi 'od kyi phreng ba can /
T02TD3635E:250b-16: 'od dpag tu med pas dbu brgyan pa bsgom par bya'o //
T02TD3635E:250b-18: aom ma h'a ba la sv'a h'a /
T02TD3635E:250b-20: stobs po che'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
